text:
> Top News The road to Kitten Bowl III paved with unspeakable cuteness Kittens play on a mini football field during the taping of "Kitten Bowl III," on Wednesday, Oct. 21, 2015, in New York. The program will be broadcast on The Hallmark Channel on Super Bowl Sunday, Feb. 7, 2016. (AP Photo/Leanne Italie) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
